The ionosphere is a mirror for the patient soul.
73 is a wish carried on radio waves.
Amateur means to serve, never to exploit.
A call sign is an identity, not just a name.
Distance is measured in watts, not kilometers.
The radio connects hearts across the horizon.
In the world of ham, the journey is the destination.
The antennae never lies about intention.
Sound travels where wires cannot reach.
A QSO is a meeting of minds across the electromagnetic field.